<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Início - Meet Space</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
   
    <nav class="bg-white shadow-sm">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between h-16">
                <div class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center">
                        <img src="../assets/logo_azul.png" alt="Logo" class="h-8 w-auto">
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:ml-8 md:flex md:space-x-8">
                        <a href="/salas" class="inline-flex items-center px-1 pt-1 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-blue-600">
                            Salas
                        </a>
                        <a href="/minhas-reservas" class="inline-flex items-center px-1 pt-1 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-blue-600">
                            Minhas Reservas
                        </a>
                        <a href="/nova-reserva" class="inline-flex items-center px-1 pt-1 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600 hover:border-b-2 hover:border-blue-600">
                            Nova Reserva
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <a href="/auth/logout" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-red-500">
                        Sair
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

   
    <div class="bg-white shadow-sm">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
                    Bem-vindo ao Meet Space
                </h1>
                <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-gray-500">
                    Gerencie suas reservas de sala de forma simples e eficiente.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
           
            <div class="bg-white overflow-hidden shadow-sm rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ml-4">
                            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Salas Disponíveis</h2>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Visualize todas as salas e suas disponibilidades em tempo real.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <a href="/salas" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700">
                            Ver Salas
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        
            <div class="bg-white overflow-hidden shadow-sm rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ml-4">
                            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Minhas Reservas</h2>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Gerencie suas reservas atuais e visualize o histórico.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <a href="/minhas-reservas" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700">
                            Ver Reservas
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            
            <div class="bg-white overflow-hidden shadow-sm rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ml-4">
                            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Nova Reserva</h2>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Faça uma nova reserva de sala de forma rápida e simples.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <a href="/nova-reserva" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700">
                            Reservar Sala
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

  <footer class="bg-white mt-12">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-6 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Sistema de Agendamento de Salas. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html> 